This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: guard dog
des:
Barking guard dog sounds to thwart off bad people and bill collectors, or tick off your noisy neighbor, should they come knocking at your door. 

This is a pure dog barking skill, ready to pounce at a moment's notice. There will be many different variations as different dog sizes are randomly played, each time you play this skill.

Because of the randomness of the barking dog effects, there may be some periods of calm, before the dogs get agitated again.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
